videos.headline: Bama uses balanced scoring, defense to rout Ole Miss
videos.description: Five score in double figures and No. 7 Alabama holds the Rebels to 2-of-24 shooting from the 3-point line to roll to an 84-62 victory.

videos.headline: Miller says No. 7 Bama exceeded game plan vs. Ole Miss
videos.description: Brandon Miller emphasizes the Tide's defensive focus and the importance of the 84-62 win against the Rebels in building their confidence for SEC play.
